WHERE C_SCHEDULE_MODIFIEDON BETWEEN DATE '2025-01-01' AND DATE '2025-01-31'

    CAST(C_FARE_COMPINSURANCE AS NUMBER(18,2)) AS C_FARE_COMPINSURANCE,

	CAST(C_ALLOCATION_ID AS NUMBER(18,0)) AS C_ALLOCATION_ID,

WHERE C_ALLOCATION_MODIFIEDON BETWEEN DATE '2025-01-01' AND  DATE '2025-01-31'

	RTSNG_PRD.RTSNG_T_ALLOCBLOCK
WHERE C_ALLOCBLOCK_MODIFIEDON BETWEEN DATE '2025-01-01' AND  DATE '2025-01-31'
